These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
House: wooden, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the wooden house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| House   | cape-cod | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
